Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:53.59,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Arashigaoka High School・(Place)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.48,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Kureha Tsubaki・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,They're beautiful in bloom, aren't they, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:12.36,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Sumika Izumino・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I think we can be together\Nhere without anyone seeing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.\NWe're not doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:28.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you, Sumika. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika, I'll never back down on my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha... Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear! There's a bear on the loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.20,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Bear"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:05.58,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Bear"\N"Bear Warning Issued・(Warning)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear got over the Wall of Severance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'll protect you, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become true\Nfriends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"NEVER BACK DOWN ON LOVE"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:49.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:04:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,One day, at the far reaches of space,\Nthe minor planet Kumaria exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:38.32,MainTop,,0,0,0,,The fragments of Kumaria became a\Nmeteor swarm that rained down on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Which made the world's bears rise up as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,They all started attacking humans!\NLike, who could've seen that coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.75,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Wall of Severance・(Place)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:57.67,MainTop,,0,0,0,,The humans built the Wall of Severance\Nto try to drive us bears from their world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,but guess what, man-made rules\Ndon't work on bears! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,We are bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears eat people. It's what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, starting today,\Nyou'll have some new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:24.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Ginko Yurishiro and Lulu Yurigasaki.\NShow them a warm welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! We've just transferred to\Nthis school, disguised as humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Muahaha! Looks like\Nnobody can tell we're bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,So many girls for me to pick from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! The whole room smells delicious, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard and eat\Nlots of girls! Right, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Ginko Yurishiro\Nhere is a bear too, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:03.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my darling, and I just {\i1}love {\i0}her! Teehee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, as I'm sure you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,bears unfortunately appeared on the\Nroads near our school this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It ought to be unthinkable for bears\Nto cross the Wall of Severance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,and enter the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,The warning has been lifted,\Nbut you mustn't be careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,As you move through the school,\Nbe sure to keep someone--a friend--with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I've finally found her. Yes, that girl smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,A delicious smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kureha, what do you\Nlike in your lunch box?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,My lunch box?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I like fried {\i1}chikuwa {\i0}in seaweed batter.\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I guess spaghetti, and {\i1}shiokara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiokara{\i0}? With lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You sound like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, maybe it smells a little\Nwhen I open my lunch box, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you've got old-man taste sometimes,\NI love you. I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you eat lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat together. We'll each take half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,There's {\i1}chikuwa {\i0}in this roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! Not fried in seaweed batter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, let's eat here every day from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that okay? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to eat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Food does taste better eaten together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:34.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! I'm hungry too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell... I want to eat her, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ginko, you're such a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, you can sink your teeth\Ninto me anywhere you'd like, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hee, I said it! I'm so daring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,The storm chased us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:31.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only the beginning. A warning that\Nit'll start with what's most precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Storm will destroy everything,\Nuntil we're worn away into nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:42.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I'll never back down on my love either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like you didn't give up on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on you--on love.\NNo matter what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,--Grrrrr.\N--Growl. I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--Grrrrr.\N--Grrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,--It smells, it smells, a delicious smell! Growl...\N--Grrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,--Grrrrr.\N--Grrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down on my love.\NI'll protect you, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been caught up in the\NInvisible Storm too, haven't you, Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.86,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Mitsuko Yurizono・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just cruel to cut down flowers in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Storm destroys\Nbeautiful, kind things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. But this has made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't keep letting these things happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki, Izumino, let's stop the\Nstorm together. We'll take a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,As class representative,\NI'm ashamed of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,for turning a blind eye until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Izumino. Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing to forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, I think we could be good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the three of us can stop the\NInvisible Storm if we work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But now we should go home for the day.\NThere was that warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I say we come early tomorrow\Nmorning and fix the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono, your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This means I'm\None of you. We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I am so happy, I got to eat a lily! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I want to eat that girl!\NWho do you mean by "that girl"? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I want to eat this girl!\NWho do you mean by "this girl"? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:20.26,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Let's go on trial! Yeah, let's go! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:30.73,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Kureha Tsubaki's House・(Place)"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep! Guess what, Mom?\NWe ate snacks together today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Great, were they yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! They're really yummy\Nwhen I eat them with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You really love her, don't you, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:55.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's why this time, the one I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'll protect with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive those bears.\NI'll {\i1}ruin {\i0}those bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Unit 103.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,We're at the flowerbed in the\NArashigaoka High School courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Lots of bear prints here, and bloodstains.\NLooks like there was a vic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We found her effects at the\Nscene--she may be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We're searching the area now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yes, we were supposed to meet.\N--Request immediate backup. I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,We were going to come early\Nand fix up the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,This mobile customer is unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard they found a shoe on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Then she must really be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:15:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently she came early\Nto work on that flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's her fault for being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,To survive, we need friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But now the next Invisible Storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's her fault for not being invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,To the bears, we're just weak prey.\NWe have to always stay in the herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, the mood of the herd\Nis what's most important!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:44.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,No way was Sumika eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a challenge from the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki,\Nif your love is true, go to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? Is Sumika safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Give yourself over to the bears,\Nand your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,The time for judgment has come, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika... Give back Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl, growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to eat her! I want to eat her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Court is in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.11,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Severance Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:51.82,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Come, the door has opened.\NThis is the land of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.95,Main,,0,0,0,,for all living things... yes, even human and bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:18:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us now pass judgment--\Nfor the sake of humans and bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.75,MainTop,,0,0,0,,LIFE Sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,For humans and bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.63,MainTop,,0,0,0,,LIFE Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.59,Main,,0,0,0,,For humans and bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.05,MainTop,,0,0,0,,LIFE Beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:19.02,MainTop,,0,0,0,,We now begin the Yuri Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:23.44,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Defendant-bears. Do you admit\Nthat you are criminal-bears?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... But, we're so {\i1}hungry{\i0}, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't back down on our love, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans and bears have a wall called Severance\Nbetween them that is not to be crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,The defendants have crossed it\Nand infiltrated the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,This is blatant overeating. They are guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, the prosecutor\Nis blatantly hostile to bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Counsel, was that intended to be an objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, even bears have to eat to live, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you telling them to starve to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,If we admit the defendants' appeal,\Nmore lives will be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Objection! He's showing\Nundue favor toward humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,This court must be a scale that\Nweighs both worlds impartially.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That is the sexy way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we can eat her then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, a Love Judgment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Very well. Defendant-bears, I ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you be invisible? Or will you eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I now declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:03.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:21.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ra-ra-rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I'm going to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is what I hope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm searching in the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Searching for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Searching for it where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me the Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono... Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We found you passed out on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What about Sumika?! Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,She hasn't been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That can't be... He said the bears\Non the roof would give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down. You were the\Nonly one lying up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Just me? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go get you something hot to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:22:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Was that a dream? But I know that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Please be okay, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Could someone be vandalizing\Nthe flowerbed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Munch, munch, munch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Human girls really do taste good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll eat them. I don't care if it's a crime, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone wreck my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are... eating someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are the transfer students...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I get it--they're bears pretending to be human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:12.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
